  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Multiplying both sides by 60 gives 15(<i>x</i> + 10) = 4(<i>x</i> + 10), so 11(<i>x</i> + 10) = 0 and <i>x</i> + 10 = 0. The value 0 lies between &minus;2 and 2.</p><p>Choices A, B, and D give ranges that do not contain 0.</p>",
